                    <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #7d8590; margin-top: 10px;">5つくらいの施設を"There is/are..."で説明してね</p>
                    <textarea class="input-field" name="hostel_tour" rows="6" placeholder="例：Welcome! There's a kitchen on the first floor. There are three bathrooms. There's WiFi in every room. There are lockers for your stuff. There's a common area upstairs."></textarea>
