                    <p style="margin-top: 15px;">質問: "Where's the kitchen?"（キッチンはどこ？）</p>
                    <input type="text" class="input-field" name="answer1" placeholder="例：There's a kitchen on the first floor">
                    <p style="margin-top: 15px;">質問: "Where are the bathrooms?"（バスルームはどこ？）</p>
                    <input type="text" class="input-field" name="answer2" placeholder="例：There are bathrooms downstairs">
